   <h1><font color="#FF0000">History</font></h1>
   <br></br>   
</center>
<ul>
<li>PHP succeeded PHP/FI
<li>PHP/FI was created by Rasmus Lerdorf in 1995
<li>PHP 3.0 1st version of PHP that resembles PHP today. Completely rewritten by Andi Gutmans and Zeev Suraski in 1997 because they found that PHP/FI was not powerful enough for their eCommerce applications.
<li>20% of web sites have PHP installed today.

